			"skeleton_king_mortal_strike"		"Once you have reached max stacks, you can cast Mortal Strike to summon Skeletons. 

They will automatically attack the nearest target and move on to the next once that target is dead.

You can use these skeletons to chain farm jungle, push lanes without your presence or chase weakened foes."
			"special_bonus_unique_wraith_king_4"		"Casts an AoE Wraithfire Blast to all nearby foes."
